<html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" /><meta http-equiv="Content-Style-Type" content="text/css" /><meta name="generator" content="Aspose.Words for .NET 13.4.0.0" /><title>Unrevised</title></head><body><div><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt 18pt 0pt 0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 12pt"><img src="data:image/png;base64," width="340" height="47" alt="" /></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 12pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:14pt">Unrevised transcript of evidence</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:14pt"> t</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:14pt">aken before</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 12pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">The Select Committee </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">o</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">n t</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:14pt; font-weight:bold">he European Union</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:14pt">Internal Market, Infrastructure, and Employment</span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:14pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:14pt">(Sub-Committee B)</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:center"><span style="font-family:'Gill Sans MT'; font-size:12pt; font-weight:normal; text-transform:none">Inquiry on</span></p><p s